metadata.name: BRAVE
metadata.description:
She stands tall, with courage in her heart,
A shining example of bravery from the start.
She faces each challenge with grace and might,
Her spirit unbreakable, shining bright.

The world may try to bring her down,
But she rises above it with a frown,
For she knows the strength she holds within,
And the power of her courage to win.

She walks with confidence and a smile,
Her bravery a beacon for all to see, a style.
She inspires those around her with each step,
Showing that bravery is not something to be kept.

So here's to this brave girl, so strong and true,
May she continue to spread her bravery like dew,
For she is a shining star, bright and bold,
And her bravery will always be worth more than gold.
